{"tid":2369532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時Quit登","createTime":"2021-01-17T08:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T23:10:46.000Z","uid":223428,"like":30,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0872e54ecea61a9dcf562c9dcc256b3c68d013e5","tid":2369532,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"學業關係，雖然和你推po同RT我好愉快，但要有靚grade同扎實嘅知識先可以幫到手足，我應該會長Quit登一段時間，為免時事台一齊推po嘅人掛心，所以特別開po通知你地一聲。<br />\n<br />\n對於我承諾過寫好故就比你睇嘅巴打，唔洗擔心，爭1.5章就完，個故應該會以protonDrive Link嘅形式喺Mewe發布，而以下<strong><span class=\"red\">其中一個</span></strong>係我嘅Mewe acc名嘅線索，而熟悉我嘅巴絲打應該可以從其他線索中搵到我：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/ac/75/a6/ac75a6759dfe58274d184c073e1f3eca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2Fac%2F75%2Fa6%2Fac75a6759dfe58274d184c073e1f3eca.jpg&h=66c9900f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRWRPUBmD3AfSd9c-Y_gq-9HHnR9BQFk_ieig&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRWRPUBmD3AfSd9c-Y_gq-9HHnR9BQFk_ieig%26usqp%3DCAU&h=800e3d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/564x/42/41/38/424138ce767c0cd3d365312bbd8c85f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F42%2F41%2F38%2F424138ce767c0cd3d365312bbd8c85f1.jpg&h=75867f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/564x/d2/4c/54/d24c5402cfb65f87dd4cf2fceb01ff3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fd2%2F4c%2F54%2Fd24c5402cfb65f87dd4cf2fceb01ff3d.jpg&h=505fbb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/62/ec/84/62ec8426bc6918bde918b28dbbfbc21f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F62%2Fec%2F84%2F62ec8426bc6918bde918b28dbbfbc21f.gif&h=8ccb8d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/564x/b6/4a/86/b64a869fe1b0083d1210c56551e9b5af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fb6%2F4a%2F86%2Fb64a869fe1b0083d1210c56551e9b5af.jpg&h=4d1b7e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/ac/c7/86/acc7869232deda9373160913cfa2ad10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2Fac%2Fc7%2F86%2Facc7869232deda9373160913cfa2ad10.jpg&h=72f12a96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前嘅承諾，因為後來發現自己諗得太天真、Data太廢，所以後來冇下文，但係都係要發布已經剔除政治相關內容的統計結果，請自己慢慢梳理：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.protonmail.com/urls/G2Z5WY33MG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.protonmail.com%2Furls%2FG2Z5WY33MG&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=647c3748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.protonmail.com/urls/G2Z5WY33MG</a> (15日後到期)<br />\n<br />\n密碼係(包大階細階英文字母同數字)：<br />\nThe most Awesome guy in the world (self-declared)<br />\n<br />\n最後都係果一句：<br />\n<blockquote>神愛世人，甚至將祂的獨生子賜給他們，叫一切信祂的，不至滅亡，反得永生。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然咁講法好屬地，但係西方世界所有講人權同自由又冇將地獄帶上人間嘅改革，特別係英國，其實都係由呢句開始。<br />\n<br />\nPo完我就登出，大家喺呢個po記得用不推文。"},{"pid":"7c2731c086ac2449656e54700d7d6ad0b8ab68e5","tid":2369532,"uid":8423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"亂b <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少咗一個推 po fd 啦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be49c92d7e84b7df8ba3ff3c7b21aca2e58b21c4","tid":2369532,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae842f08c70daa0de9871244d701e7c7838e441d","tid